item.title: 【Requests】[REQ PDF] - Taylor Swift – ‘1989 (Taylor's Version)’ Crystal Skies Blue Edition CD booklet HQ scans
item.description:
Hello,

I am wondering if anybody with the standard Crystal Skies Blue CD of Taylor Swift's 1989 (Taylor's Version) has or would please be willing to scan the entire CD booklet for me. This includes the front cover, all 18 interior pages, the back, CD disc, and both sides of the inlay. I am attempting to make a digital version/replica to share with everyone, so I please needed the highest quality possible.

Thank you!
